fulltitle: Church Committee: Covert Action in Chile, 1963-73 (BC.5)
title: Church Committee: Covert Action in Chile, 1963-73 (BC.5)
description:
'Our Hidden History' Audiobooks: https://sellfy.com/OurHiddenHistory More Church Committee Reports: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBINnEpNu5u5DDKZr3zRDb9v_Q2pV55dA ---- This is The Church Committee's "Covert Action in Chile 1963-73" (Part Five: "Preliminary Conclusions"). The official name of the Church Committee was "Senate Select Committee To Study Governmental Operations With Respect to Intelligence Activities". A copy of the report may also be found on the U.S. Senate Select Committee on Intelligence web site: http://www.intelligence.senate.gov/pdfs94th/94chile.pdf

V. Preliminary Conclusions
    A. Covert Action and U.S. Foreign Policy
    B. Executive Command and Control of Major Covert Action
    C. The Role of Congress
    D. Intelligence Judgments and Covert Operations
    E. Major Covert Action Programs

This audio recreation was narrated by John Hawkes (https://www.fiverr.com/johnhawkes) and produced by D. Giglio for 'Our Hidden History'

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
